BLUSH PLACEMENTS (5 different ways to apply blush)

Hello, I'm Agatha! 😊

I'm here with you the different ways you can apply blush as well as what blush placement suits your face shape the best! I hope you enjoyed watching the video and learned a thing or two from me. Please let me know if you want more makeup tutorial like this 🥰

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching :)

If you have suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

Let's be friends!
